    "4004809": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Tower of the Void",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "I am the Jibashiri Kurai. Are you here to help solve the problem of these small orbs of thunder?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What problem is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "Ah, yes, when I went to Narukami Island to conduct an exchange previously, I used a secret technique to capture some strange objects."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "I think the academic name for it is an Electro Seele. Or something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "They fly all over the place, and numb all the people living here. It's quite vexing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What do you need solved?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "Well, the issue of those Electro Cells, of course."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "Between you and me, I have no idea what to do with them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "Vishaps and villains, I can master, but these little gadgets are way beyond me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "How am I supposed to stop them from moving?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "See you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kurai",
                    "T": "See you. If you know how, please help me solve this electric ball problem."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
